sentence: what is the highest point in each state whose lowest point is sea level ?
sentence-with-vars: what is the highest point in each state whose lowest point is sea level ?
sql: select highlow.highest_point , highlow.state_name from highlow where highlow.lowest_elevation = 0 ;
sql-with-vars: select highlow.highest_point , highlow.state_name from highlow where highlow.lowest_elevation = number0 ;
